{"tid":1666790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際戰線！加拿大手足今日記得投票！","createTime":"2019-10-21T06:32:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T09:57:19.000Z","uid":237133,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"72751bb55dda71a86941d896cb80451e7051e74f","tid":1666790,"uid":237133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:32:04.000Z","msg":"今日係加拿大聯邦大選，338個國會議席會重選！<br />\n<br />\n投票須知懶人包：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/canada-voter-guide-2019-federal-election-1.5260336\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fcanada-voter-guide-2019-federal-election-1.5260336&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERSEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=8d65da2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/canada-voter-guide-2019-federal-election-1.5260336</a><br />\n<br />\n今次聯邦選舉係歷來形勢最接近一次，選前兩大黨民意調查相距只係一至兩個百分點<br />\n<br />\n除咗國內民生事項，今次投票亦都成為國際戰線一部份：<br />\n<br />\n華為進入美國已經失敗，但北美仍然有加拿大呢個潛在市場，華為已經參與加拿大鄉村網絡工程！正在虎視眈眈全國網絡！加拿大手足要比個清晰意見聯邦政府！<br />\n<br />\n華為+加拿大&gt;&gt;&gt;孟晚舟事件<br />\n<br />\n加拿大某國移民所構成嘅社會問題，港生喺大學搞示威同連儂牆時一定會明白！<br />\n<br />\n我地需要多d國際戰友！下任總理會否Stand with HK???<br />\n<br />\n加拿大手足記得今日投票！！！"},{"pid":"e9fd43247b9f14a268d3a09a61596a1e56268a8e","tid":1666790,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:32:27.000Z","msg":"不如全港黨鐵靜坐聲討721啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665580</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa50ad5d2d594d6daf0e7d1531c601e0940cc4b4","tid":1666790,"uid":237133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:32:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e37ae6c749b9dbd8c73134c88f2a11c4eb05f43","tid":1666790,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:33:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dae70077910de80081411a51547ac19f82d2d853","tid":1666790,"uid":237133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:38:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"408825d50a2f6268e3a655ff6618c2f2b16df58d","tid":1666790,"uid":237133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:43:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae01ca0981cb88ade1efe7f0337347d3408168ae","tid":1666790,"uid":265168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:44:28.000Z","msg":"屌晒你地<br />\n尋晚開<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">行動po</span>到而家都仲未上到熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢單野新鮮滾熱辣 connect全世界<br />\n依家就係最好時機！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地fight for freedom<br />\n我無宗教信仰 但我有宗教自由 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n早喺六月已經有宗教俾popo當眾侮辱 <br />\n打壓宗教自由之餘亦都對各個宗教不尊重<br />\n<br />\n睇原po！<br />\n既然我哋係fight for freedom<br />\n咁我哋更加係時候聲援被打壓宗教自由嘅人！<br />\n快啲一齊討論！<br />\n<br />\n係時候搞個 尊重宗教自由大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665685\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665685</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6d992d3cb30841061d3761af8c706d22516137e4","tid":1666790,"uid":237133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:48:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2bfd4e0af9695deacafb4c14775371cf86e274ec","tid":1666790,"uid":237133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:51:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"08b1902c2fb3a3217e7ce39c0bfbab6f47396913","tid":1666790,"uid":258748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:57:32.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"222e46a1a6ecde168c7a956f926dd32ceaed00a3","tid":1666790,"uid":256837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:07:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https: