"今日係加拿大聯邦大選，338個國會議席會重選！<br />\n<br />\n投票須知懶人包：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/canada-voter-guide-2019-federal-election-1.5260336\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fcanada-voter-guide-2019-federal-election-1.5260336&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERSEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=8d65da2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/canada-voter-guide-2019-federal-election-1.5260336</a><br />\n<br />\n今次聯邦選舉係歷來形勢最接近一次，選前兩大黨民意調查相距只係一至兩個百分點<br />\n<br />\n除咗國內民生事項，今次投票亦都成為國際戰線一部份：<br />\n<br />\n華為進入美國已經失敗，但北美仍然有加拿大呢個潛在市場，華為已經參與加拿大鄉村網絡工程！正在虎視眈眈全國網絡！加拿大手足要比個清晰意見聯邦政府！<br />\n<br />\n華為+加拿大&gt;&gt;&gt;孟晚舟事件<br />\n<br />\n加拿大某國移民所構成嘅社會問題，港生喺大學搞示威同連儂牆時一定會明白！<br />\n<br />\n我地需要多d國際戰友！下任總理會否Stand with HK???<br />\n<br />\n加拿大手足記得今日投票！！！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:54:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:14:20.000Z","msg":"願意stand with HK，即係同香港抗爭者同一陣線，願意放棄部份眼前一d所謂嘅經濟利益，去追求民主自由嘅核心價值，而呢個先至係真正嘅利益"},{"pid":"7aceaece0ec4ffbcdefe5d44e11c8c1dda0e9546","tid":1666790,"uid":237133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:17:31.000Z","msg":"澳洲已經開始收緊新聞自由，加拿大人要小心"},{"pid":"19711f76fc91223403cdb1f434c87f762ce59a0d","tid":1666790,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:18:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74d15eee42af2b9a650f555890b9f67acd91c2d5","tid":1666790,"uid":237133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:36:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0cd164918bda6ca05fbc858c4e796b39c11cd3b5","tid":1666790,"uid":221428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:02:55.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"be90de6b6aa1a2a2b89c0c0fe5884ad6bac4bcaf","tid":1666790,"uid":221428,"like":0,"di